Class ImmutablePosition

java.lang.Object
net.apartium.cocoabeans.space.Position
net.apartium.cocoabeans.space.ImmutablePosition
@AvailableSince("0.0.22") public class ImmutablePosition extends Position
Immutable version of Position When the position is modified, a new Position is created and the original one is left unchanged
